{"tid":1528943,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以對準政府官員同警員","createTime":"2019-09-01T15:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T20:46:06.000Z","uid":219463,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"36674b30bd81c19becbc63647cc5aeb5be355e1d","tid":1528943,"uid":219463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:37:21.000Z","msg":"家母有未知疾病<br />\n睇咗好耐醫生都唔知咩病<br />\n睇幾個專科都未有用<br />\n要周圍去幾間診所驗依樣驗嗰樣<br />\n聽日仲要過海睇醫生<br />\n啱啱佢問我可以點過去<br />\n見手足討論聽日點幫大家罷工<br />\n我都唔知點答佢好<br />\n返少日工係唔使死<br />\n但仲有人唔係返工而需要交通<br />\n之前佢要日日去診所打針<br />\n咁啱撞正上次大三罷封路<br />\n差啲就打唔到抗生素針，好彩嗰次近行到去個醫生幫佢打埋針先拉閘<br />\n<br />\n見過政府，黨鐵，黑警搞到人地見唔到親人最後一面<br />\n我唔想有一日會因為示威而見到有病人受難<br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"5a54345c90a31d2ed33bb932bb31c87eb826ccc9","tid":1528943,"uid":300554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:42:33.000Z","msg":"緊急工種會維持有限度工作<br />\n請為任何形式的罷工未雨綢繆作好準備<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3隻眼 6條命 900被捕 無數斷手斷腳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831黨鐵恐襲傷者消息全無</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n九二九三大三罷！<br />\n設死線 升級持續罷工<br />\n日日罷工 日日入機場<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【升級罷工】EndGame＝全面開啟升級抗爭</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">網民問卷調查報告 我們在這沉痛的晚上公佈</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1525035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1525035</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bVP4X9g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbVP4X9g.jpg&h=c7d56cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y5iA4Pi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY5iA4Pi.jpg&h=b866962b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hL7VVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hL7VVY.jpg&h=fc849ad9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad7a5